Class RowDescriptorBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.apache.cayenne.access.jdbc.RowDescriptorBuilder
public class RowDescriptorBuilder
extends Object
A builder class that helps to assemble RowDescriptor instances from various types of inputs.

3.0
